{"tid":275832,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"長江基建(01038.HK)降每手買賣單位至500股","createTime":"2017-06-08T10:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T10:37:56.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af1e61b4e9d3c003ebb5f614314bedb5d09c84a7","tid":275832,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"長江基建(<a href=\"http://01038.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01038.HK&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjncjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b913752a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01038.HK</a>)宣佈，自六月三十日起，股份每手買賣單位將由一千股更改為五百股。以中午收市價67.65元計算，即每手入場費將由六萬七千幾元，減少至三萬三千幾元。<br />\n<br />\n長建表示，降低每手買賣單位，可提高股份的流通性，並不會導致股東的相關權利有改變。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_368&amp;itemid=944697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_368%26itemid%3D944697&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjncjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=16155429\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_368&amp;itemid=944697</a>"}]}